summary: The Dead City is a large underground city, the population has been cursed by a wizard into becoming undead.
descriptionHtml:
The Dead City is a large underground city, the population has been cursed by a wizard into becoming undead.
There is no real quest to undertake here, explore, loot and try to escape with what you can.
Features a large and fully explorable city with about 80 interior cells, plus a few new skins and textures.
author: Richard Valongo
